== Redmine Zendesk plugin

This plugin will update Zendesk tickets whenever an associated Redmine issue is updated.

== Installation

1. Copy the plugin directory into the plugins directory
2. Run bundle install to install plugin dependency gem (zendesk api client)
3. Run rake redmine:plugins:migrate RAILS_ENV=production
4. Add a Custom Field for the Zendesk ticket number(s)
5. Configure the Zendesk plugin from the 'Admin -> Plugins' screen.
